Solver                         Trail                         Clause store
  │                              │                               │
  │ analyzeConflict(C*)          │                               │
  │ learned = *C                 │                               │
  │ while (#lits on currLevel > 1):
  │   resolveLit = youngest lit on currentLevel from Trail ─────▶ getTrail()
  │   reason_idx = getReasonIndexOfVar(resolveLit.var) ◀─────────┘
  │   reason = clauses[reason_idx]
  │   learned = resolve(learned, reason) über resolveLit
  │ end
  │ assertLit = einziges lit auf currentLevel
  │ backjump = max level( learned.lits \ {assertLit} )
  │ return (learned, backjump, assertLit)